      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t我对日本了解相对不多，日本的葱油，你们国家没有NGO和宗教团体在各个街区寻找和帮助穷人吗？再退一步，食物银行得有吧?<br/>\n这不是责难，我只是问是什么情况？<br/>\n<br/>\n--------<br/>\n查了一下wikipedia，<br/>\n<blockquote>According to the Ministry of Agriculture, Forestry and Fisheries in Japan, the number of such organizations stood at 178 in the FY2022 through March, marking a significant increase from the 120 seen two years earlier. As of 2022, there is at least one food bank organization in every prefecture in Japan. The importance of food banks has become more recognized during the Covid-19 pandemic. </blockquote><br/>\n看起来也不是很多，但每个都道府县都有，也不至于就在那等死啊。那估计网上的人说她患有厌食症是有道理的。\t\t</div>",
